info.gridworld.character

Class CharacterU

  • java.lang.Object
    • info.gridworld.character.CharacterU
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    UnitArcher, UnitAssassin, UnitHealer, UnitVanguard, UnitWarrior

    public abstract class CharacterU
extends java.lang.Object
    A base template for all of the different characters. Includes methods to access back-end data structures as well as GUI elements from the user input.
    Version:
    May 29, 2017
    Author:
    Eric K, Period: 1, Assignment: NetTileGW, Sources: None
